      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept car in good overall condition. It shows nicely inside and out, with a solid interior, a good exterior appearance, and the kind of normal cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle rather than anything excessive. Everything presents as cared for, and a buyer should expect a dependable, presentable car that still has plenty of life left.",
