    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and opportunity over cosmetics. A practical option for basic commuting, a project, or a spare vehicle, with honest value for the money.",
