      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with some life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants cheap wheels, a handy project, or a practical runaround. It shows its age and will suit a buyer who understands used cars, but it still has plenty of potential for the right person. Priced to sell and offered honestly\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels honest and usable. Not a cosmetic showpiece, but that is exactly what makes it a great entry point for someone who wants a budget-friendly driver, weekend wrenching project, or platform to build. A straightforward car with character, serviceable hardware, and real potential.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Honest poor-condition driver with wear, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence that still turns heads in a parking lot and the sort of honest, lived-in character that makes it feel like more than just transportation. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone looking for a budget-friendly ride with personality, or a hands-on owner who appreciates the charm and potential in a well-traveled machine. There\u2019s a lot to like here for the right buyer: a distinctive look, a comfortable cabin, and the chance to own something with story, substance, and room to make it your own.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and would best suit someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it still offers solid value for the money and a chance to get on the road without a major investment. A smart budget buy for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone needing inexpensive transportation.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
